# Fucking Hell (Chapman)

Fucking Hell is a 2008 installation artwork by Jake and Dinos Chapman depicting a monumental battle of miniature skeletons, Nazis, and others. It is a recreation of their 1998-2000 Hell, which was lost in a fire. It sold for Â£7.5 million.
